d role-filter gating. (~3h)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-003** [T1] Implement R1 Metric Accent: per-beat-position velocity multiplier applied only to non-grid-locked melodic/accent voices. (~3h)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-004** [T1] Implement R2 Phrase Arch (Todd/KTH): parabolic tempo + loudness arch over each phrase, modulated by section envelope. (~3h)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-005** [T1] Implement R3 Agogic Accent: lengthen + emphasize notes at local contour apex or harmonic-charge peak. (~3h)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-006** [T1] Implement R4 Duration Contrast: exaggerate short-vs-long by log(dur_ratio_to_median), melodic roles only, capped at ┬▒10%. (~3h)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-007** [T1] Implement R5 Final Ritardando: FribergŌĆōSundberg square-root tempo curve over last 20ŌĆō30% of cadential phrases. (~3h)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-008** [T1] Implement R6 Punctuation + Breath: lengthen terminal note at phrase boundary and insert breath silence of breath_after_ms. (~3h)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-009** [T1] Implement R7 Articulation Shaping: per-note gate-time by style (legato 0.95ŌĆō1.02, normal 0.7ŌĆō0.85, staccato 0.3ŌĆō0.5, staccatissimo 0.15ŌĆō0.25) with contour adjustments. (~3h)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-010** [T1] Implement R8 Microtiming Polish: per-note Gaussian jitter Žā=3 ms on melodic, 1 ms on ostinato, 0 ms on grid-locked machine voices. (~3h)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-*Subtotal: ~27 hours*\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+*Subtotal: ~30 hours*\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+### Sprint 2: Quality Scoring\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+**Depends on:** Sprint 0 (Versioning System), Sprint 1 (Quality Scoring)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-011** [T1] Implement R12 Sensor-to-Intent Aggregation Matrix: smoothed IIR + hysteresis ŌåÆ aggregate intentions (global_energy, global_restraint, global_brightness). (~3h) ŌåÆ deps: T-001\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-012** [T1] Implement bounded reactive delta track in scheduler with per-parameter modulation caps. (~3h) ŌåÆ deps: T-001