 - Added depth-2 end-to-end accompaniment test coverage (frac-0055): `tests/test_accompaniment.py` now ships a new `TestAccompanimentEndToEnd` class that drives the existing Korsakov accompaniment public surface (`DensityTracker`, `select_accompaniment_type`, `breathing_swell`, `should_transition_gradually`, `should_pedal`, `pedal_note`, `get_pattern`, and the six pattern generators) through end-to-end multi-step pytest methods. The new tests sweep the documented density bands and verify the inverse-density rule, iterate every pattern type 1-6 to assert non-empty events with positive amps/releases, sweep `breathing_swell` over rest/active/edge inputs, walk full phrase boundaries through `should_pedal` + `pedal_note`, run the dense-melody and resting-melody pipelines end-to-end through a synthetic `DensityTracker` window, and pin a six-bar composer loop. A `test_test_accompaniment_reaches_depth_two` gate test asserts the file's fractal classification is at least depth 2. Existing `TestDensityTracker`, `TestSelectAccompanimentType`, `TestPatterns`, `TestPedalPoint`, `TestBreathing`, and `TestTransition` assertions are preserved unchanged; `tests/test_accompaniment_depth.py`, `tests/test_smoke_narrative_script.py`, and the startup identity anchors remain green.
 
 - Added depth-2 pytest collection gate reports (frac-0054): `tests/conftest.py` now exposes a frozen `CollectionGateDecision` dataclass plus `collection_gate_decisions`, `apply_collection_gate_decisions`, and `summarize_collection_gate_decisions` so tests and diagnostics can inspect live/host-specific marker gates with enabled state, skip reason, matched count, skipped count, and JSON-safe totals. Existing `--run-live-modal`, `--run-live-replicate`, `live_modal`, `live_replicate`, and `cypherclaw_e2e` behavior is preserved: Modal/Replicate live tests skip by default unless opted in, and CypherClaw e2e skips on CI. `tests/test_conftest_depth.py` pins hook registration, default and CI gate behavior, JSON-safe summaries, and fractal depth >= 2; startup identity anchors and the full validation gate remain green.
